data.description: Welcome to your charming single-story home nestled in Spanish Fork. This 2-bed, 1-bath home sits on a third of an acre, offering ample space for your dreams to grow. With RV parking and potential room for a second structure, the possibilities are endless. The home features a recently remodeled kitchen and bath, along with newer carpet, siding, and windows, ensuring a fresh, inviting space for you to enjoy. Whether you're envisioning a mother-in-law suite or seeking a passive income opportunity, this property is ready to make your ideas a reality. Don't miss out on the chance to call this space your own.
